moji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打散工過活<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之前番過ft但都受唔住壓力 我認我廢j</blockquote><br />\nI know that feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又唔敢唔返</blockquote><br />\n我會諗到將來好差<br />\n自己係垃圾，唔會搵到好工<br />\n番工都1999咁<br />\n唔知生存做咩，都唔會做到自己想做既野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 死唔去又唔知係度做咩"},{"pid":"132963b6558d77871971e92c6e501da88766b66a","tid":127752,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T10:47:34.000Z","msg":"係單人咩？<br />\n我個陣成日同人吹水好開心<br />\n係入面又識到老師大學生 咩人都有<br />\n出到黎都仲有contact"},{"pid":"038125fa059800bd844d1557a5945c9b27166651","tid":127752,"uid":7321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T14:36:43.000Z","msg":"原來咁多巴打試過因為情緒問題入緊症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bc6d183b7dc77c7dc24cf7a51e0eac255a5577d","tid":127752,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T14:42:01.000Z","msg":"私家精神科考唔考慮？<br />\n我睇過係ok的，個診所好舒服好靚，<br />\n會播啲好柔嘅音樂令你個人放鬆啲。"},{"pid":"a593bce13e1f7e12a3504b5f5f09acf2b41c7aea","tid":127752,"uid":20116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T21:59:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>私家精神科考唔考慮？<br />\n我睇過係ok的，個診所好舒服好靚，<br />\n會播啲好柔嘅音樂令你個人放鬆啲。</blockquote><br />\n幾錢左右？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b24feecb1198276033beb0fbf89a329f53e55076","tid":127752,"uid":7321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T05:47:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>私家精神科考唔考慮？<br />\n我睇過係ok的，個診所好舒服好靚，<br />\n會播啲好柔嘅音樂令你個人放鬆啲。</blockquote><br />\n那有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" 