quote>我諗公立有醫生referral都要3個月<br />\n出面唔只Tim<br />\n加上真係好少心理學家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你預經社工轉個d會仲耐<br />\n當然有方法7日內見到啦<br />\n想知再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n求教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n入去急症室話自己想死<br />\n然後會叫你自願留院<br />\n之後就有得見<br />\n當然你要預留係醫院起碼一個星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢位巴打有啲經歷喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 知得咁清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當時係發生起你身上定係身邊既人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97ab2249d6cfcc08420b46d433b40a1b509ce408","tid":127752,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T20:44:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.swd.gov.hk/tc/index/site_faqs/page_clinicalps/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.swd.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Findex%2Fsite_faqs%2Fpage_clinicalps%2F&d=Mrz8gheyF4cbCiJyPb%2FMEzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=42b69c65\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.swd.gov.hk/tc/index/site_faqs/page_clinicalps/</a><br />\n<br />\n第二個問題果到有答案，<br />\n<br />\n唔好好似上面位巴打咁衝去急症室叫自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n會有醫療紀錄，唔好做傻事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：未試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有機會真係想試返次睇吓會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce4d5e2b9248659f1226ece26d22566d71ea4f27","tid":127752,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T00:47:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>私家精神科考唔考慮？<br />\n我睇過係ok的，個診所好舒服好靚，<br />\n會播啲好柔嘅音樂令你個人放鬆啲。</blockquote><br />\n幾錢左